  (110523, 12092, 'I-I think I shall visit him Of course, he''s mad too Oh, but I don''t want to go among mad people Oh, you can''t help that Most everyone''s mad here You may have noticed...', NULL),
  (110524, 12092, 'But I thought there was plenty of room Ah, but it''s very rude to sit down without being invited I''ll say it''s rude.', NULL),
